searchQuery.query:
source logs 
| filter json.trace_id != null
| groupby json.trace_id as Trace agg count() as Logs
| join (source spans
    	   | groupby traceID as Trace agg count() as Spans) using Trace into APM
| choose Trace, Logs, APM.Spans as Spans, `{round(100*Logs/APM.Spans,2)}%` as Ratio

source logs last 6h
| groupby $l.applicationname as Application, $l.subsystemname as Subsystem agg 
		count() as Logs, 
		count_if($m.severity> INFO) as HS_Logs
| filter HS_Logs > 0
| create HS_Pct from `{round(100*HS_Logs/Logs,2)}%`
| orderby HS_Logs desc

source logs last 6h
| filter cx_rum.longtask_context.duration > 0
| groupby  case_lessthan {
    cx_rum.longtask_context.duration:num,
    101 -> 'Good (0-100)',
    201 -> 'Med (101-200)',
    301 -> 'Bad (201-300)',
    _ -> 'Investigate (301 - *)'} as Range agg count()

source logs last 6h
| filter cx_metadata.faas_name != null
| groupby cx_metadata.faas_name as Lambda, cx_metadata.faas_execution as execeution_Id agg 
    count() as Logs, 
    min($m.timestamp) as Start, 
    max($m.timestamp) as End 
| create Duration from End-Start
| convert Duration:num
#| groupby Lambda aggregate 
#    round(sum(Duration),2):interval.roundInterval('us') as Sum_Exec, 
#    round(avg(Duration),2):interval.roundInterval('us') as Avg_Exec, 
#    round(percentile(0.95,Duration),2):interval.roundInterval('us') as P95

source logs last 6h
| filter $l.subsystemname == 'paymentservice' 
| filter body ~ 'InvalidCreditCard' || pay_transaction.amount:num > 0
| create Trans_usd from 
  case_equals {
        pay_transaction.currency,
        'USD'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 1,
        'EUR'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 1.04,
        'JPY'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 0.0066,
        'CAD'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 0.69}
| groupby $m.timestamp / 1h as Time aggregate 
        count_if($m.severity != ERROR) as Successfull_Transactions, 
        count_if(body ~ 'InvalidCreditCard') as Err_Transactions,  
        `${round(sum(Trans_usd),2)}` as Total_Revenue, 
        round(avg(Trans_usd),2) as Avg_Revenue
| create Lost_Revenue from `${round(Avg_Revenue*Err_Transactions,2)}`
| orderby Time

source logs last 6h
| filter $l.subsystemname == 'paymentservice' 
| filter pay_transaction.amount:num > 0
| create Trans_usd from 
  case_equals {
        pay_transaction.currency,
        'USD'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 1,
        'EUR'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 1.04,
        'JPY'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 0.0066,
        'CAD'   -> pay_transaction.amount:num * 0.69}
| groupby $m.timestamp/1h as Time, pay_transaction.cc as Credit_Card agg 
    count() as Transactions, 
    `${round(sum(Trans_usd),2)}` as Total_Revenue,
    `${round(avg(Trans_usd),2)}` as Avg_Revenue
| orderby Time

| filter http_resp_status != null
# Group http responses and name the group + aggregate the counts and name the count

source logs
| groupby $l.subsystemname as Subsystem agg 
		count() as Logs, 
		count_if($m.severity> INFO) as HS_Logs
| join (source logs timeshifted -1d
    | groupby $l.subsystemname as Subsystem agg 
		count() as Logs, 
		count_if($m.severity> INFO) as HS_Logs
    | filter HS_Logs > 0) on left=>$d.Subsystem == right=>$d.Subsystem into Yesterday
| join (source logs timeshifted -7d
    | groupby $l.subsystemname as Subsystem agg 
		count() as Logs, 
		count_if($m.severity> INFO) as HS_Logs
    | filter HS_Logs > 0) on left=>$d.Subsystem == right=>$d.Subsystem into LastWeek
| create HS_Pct from round(HS_Logs*100/Logs,2)
| create HS_Pct_Yesterday from round(Yesterday.HS_Logs*100/Yesterday.Logs,2)
| create HS_Pct_LastWeek from round(LastWeek.HS_Logs*100/LastWeek.Logs,2)
| choose Subsystem, Logs, HS_Pct, HS_Pct_Yesterday, HS_Pct_LastWeek
| orderby HS_Pct desc
